<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.css"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick-theme.min.css"/>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick.min.js"></script>
    <title>Planer - Plastic Ocean Recovery</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="website icon" type="png"
    href="/image/logonew.png">
    <style>
   /* Global Styles */


/* Header Styles */
header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1abc9c, #16a085);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 2.5em;
    color: white;
}

header p {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

/* Report Section Styles */
.report-section {
    background-color: white;
    margin: 20px auto;
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.report-section:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.report-section h2 {
    color: #2980b9;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.statistic ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.statistic li {
    background-color: #f4f9f9;
    margin: 10px 0;
    padding: 15px;
    border-left: 5px solid #1abc9c;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

/* Impact Graphic */
.impact-graphic {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

/* Form Styles */
.container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 30px auto;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.container h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.form-group {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.form-group label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #2980b9;
}

.form-group input, 
.form-group select, 
.form-group textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #a0d2eb;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
}

.form-group input:focus, 
.form-group select:focus, 
.form-group textarea:focus {
    border-color: #1abc9c;
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(26, 188, 156, 0.5);
}

.submit-btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1abc9c, #16a085);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.submit-btn:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a085, #1abc9c);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .report-section, .container {
        margin: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    header {
        padding: 20px 10px;
    }

    header h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
    }
}

/* Scrollbar Styles */
::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 10px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: #f1f1f1;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: #1abc9c;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
    background: #16a085;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header', {
    }) %>

<br><br>

    <header>
        <h1>Ocean Waste Report 2024</h1>
        <p>Comprehensive Analysis of Marine Pollution and Environmental Impact</p>
    </header>

    <div class="report-section">
        <h2>Global Ocean Waste Overview</h2>
        <p>Marine pollution continues to be a critical environmental challenge. Our comprehensive research reveals alarming statistics about waste accumulation in the world's oceans.</p>
        
        <div class="statistic">
            <p>Key Statistics:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Approximately <strong>8 million tons</strong> of plastic enter the oceans annually</li>
                <li>Over <strong>5.25 trillion</strong> pieces of plastic debris currently exist in the ocean</li>
                <li>Marine waste affects <strong>661 marine species</strong> known to be impacted by pollution</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="impact-graphic">
        <h2>Visual Representation of Ocean Waste Impact</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="report-section">
        <h2>Waste Composition Breakdown</h2>
        <p>Our analysis shows the primary types of waste found in marine environments:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Plastic Packaging: 38%</li>
            <li>Food Wrappers: 22%</li>
            <li>Fishing Gear: 15%</li>
            <li>Bottles and Containers: 12%</li>
            <li>Other Waste: 13%</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="report-section">
        <h2>Environmental Consequences</h2>
        <p>The continuous accumulation of waste in our oceans leads to severe environmental challenges:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Destruction of marine ecosystems</li>
            <li>Microplastic contamination in food chains</li>
            <li>Harm to marine wildlife</li>
            <li>Potential long-term climate impacts</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Ocean Waste Report Form</h1>
        <form action="#" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Full Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="location">Location of Waste Observation</label>
                <input type="text" id="location" name="location" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="date">Date of Observation</label>
                <input type="date" id="date" name="date" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="waste-type">Type of Waste</label>
                <select id="waste-type" name="waste-type" required>
                    <option value="">Select Waste Type</option>
                    <option value="plastic">Plastic</option>
                    <option value="fishing-gear">Fishing Gear</option>
                    <option value="industrial">Industrial Waste</option>
                    <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="description">Detailed Description</label>
                <textarea id="description" name="description" placeholder="Describe the waste you observed in detail" required></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="estimated-quantity">Estimated Quantity</label>
                <select id="estimated-quantity" name="estimated-quantity" required>
                    <option value="">Select Quantity</option>
                    <option value="small">Small (Few pieces)</option>
                    <option value="medium">Medium (Significant amount)</option>
                    <option value="large">Large (Extensive coverage)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit Report</button>
        </form>
    </div>      
    <%- include('../partials/footer', {
    }) %>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $('.slick-slider').slick({
            dots: true,
            infinite: true,
            speed: 800,
            fade: true,
            cssEase: 'cubic-bezier(0.7, 0, 0.3, 1)',
            autoplay: true,
            autoplaySpeed: 5000,
            pauseOnHover: false,
            arrows: true,
            draggable: true,
            swipe: true,
            touchThreshold: 10,
            waitForAnimate: true,
            responsive: [
                {
                    breakpoint: 768,
                    settings: {
                        arrows: false
                    }
                }
            ]
        });
    
        window.onscroll = function() {
        const navbar = document.getElementById("navbar");
        
        if (window.scrollY > 0) { // Jika posisi scroll lebih dari 0
            navbar.classList.add("scrolled");
        } else { // Jika posisi scroll di bagian atas halaman
            navbar.classList.remove("scrolled");
        }
        };
    
            $(document).ready(function(){
                $('.plastic-grid').slick({
                    dots: true,
                    infinite: true,
                    speed: 500,
                    slidesToShow: 3,
                    slidesToScroll: 1,
                    autoplay: true,
                    autoplaySpeed: 900,
                    responsive: [
                        {
                            breakpoint: 1024,
                            settings: {
                                slidesToShow: 2,
                                slidesToScroll: 1
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            breakpoint: 600,
                            settings: {
                                slidesToShow: 1,
                                slidesToScroll: 1
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                });
            });
    
                $(document).ready(function(){
                $('.slick-slider').slick({
                dots: true,
                infinite: true,
                speed: 800,
                fade: true,
                cssEase: 'cubic-bezier(0.7, 0, 0.3, 1)',
                autoplay: true,
                autoplaySpeed: 5000,
                pauseOnHover: false,
                arrows: true,
                draggable: true,
                swipe: true,
                touchThreshold: 10,
                waitForAnimate: true,
                responsive: [
                    {
                        breakpoint: 768,
                        settings: {
                            arrows: false
                        }
                    }
                ]
            });
    
            window.onscroll = function() {
            const navbar = document.getElementById("navbar");
            
            if (window.scrollY > 0) { // Jika posisi scroll lebih dari 0
                navbar.classList.add("scrolled");
            } else { // Jika posisi scroll di bagian atas halaman
                navbar.classList.remove("scrolled");
            }
        };
            // Add smooth transition for slide content
            $('.slick-slider').on('beforeChange', function(event, slick, currentSlide, nextSlide){
                $(this).find('.slide-content').css('opacity', '0');
            });
            
            $('.slick-slider').on('afterChange', function(event, slick, currentSlide){
                $(this).find('.slick-active .slide-content').css('opacity', '1');
            });
            });
    
        // Add smooth transition for slide content
        $('.slick-slider').on('beforeChange', function(event, slick, currentSlide, nextSlide){
            $(this).find('.slide-content').css('opacity', '0');
        });
        
        $('.slick-slider').on('afterChange', function(event, slick, currentSlide){
            $(this).find('.slick-active .slide-content').css('opacity', '1');
        });
        });
        </script>
</body>
</html>